A.1. **"The Software"**: Refers to the Svitlogics project in its totality: all source code (frontend and backend), proprietary system prompts, architectural design, the Svitlogics Design System, the Svitlogics Writing System, and all related assets within this repository.
A.2. **"Generated Analysis"**: Refers to any and all output from the Software, irrespective of format.
A.3. **"The Author"**: Refers to Eugene Kozlovsky.
A.4. **"Derivative Work"**: Any software that incorporates, is based upon, or derives from any part of the Software.
A.5. **"Malicious Use"**: Any use of the Software for purposes detailed in Article C.1.

