B.1. **NO WARRANTY OF ANY KIND**: THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "WITH ALL FAULTS". THE AUTHOR DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, EXPRESS, IMPLIED, STATUTORY, OR OTHERWISE, TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW. THIS INCLUDES, BUT IS NOT LIMITED TO, ANY WARRANTY OF PERFORMANCE, ACCURACY, RELIABILITY, SECURITY, OR NONINFRINGEMENT.

B.2. **GENERATED ANALYSIS IS NOT FACT**: THE GENERATED ANALYSIS IS THE PROBABILISTIC OUTPUT OF A THIRD-PARTY LARGE LANGUAGE MODEL. IT IS NOT A STATEMENT OF FACT, A "TRUTH VERDICT," OR PROFESSIONAL ADVICE. IT IS AN EDUCATIONAL ARTIFACT FOR ANALYSIS. **RELIANCE ON THE GENERATED ANALYSIS FOR ANY DECISION-MAKING IS STRICTLY AND ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN RISK.**

B.3. **CATASTROPHIC RISK ASSUMPTION**: YOU, THE USER, ASSUME THE ENTIRE RISK AS TO THE QUALITY AND PERFORMANCE OF THE SOFTWARE. IN NO EVENT SHALL THE AUTHOR BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES WHATSOEVER (INCLUDING, WITHOUT LIMITATION, DAMAGES FOR LOSS OF BUSINESS PROFITS, BUSINESS INTERRUPTION, LOSS OF BUSINESS INFORMATION, OR ANY OTHER PECUNIARY LOSS) ARISING OUT OF THE USE OR INABILITY TO USE THE SOFTWARE, EVEN IF THE AUTHOR HAS BEEN ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES.

