D.1. **GOVERNING LAW**: This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the substantive laws of Ukraine.

D.2. **EXCLUSIVE JURISDICTION**: The Parties irrevocably agree that the competent courts of Kyiv, Ukraine shall have exclusive jurisdiction to settle any dispute or claim that arises out of or in connection with this Agreement.

